, Mortimer, Riegelhuth, Waller|Lewis Clark, Julie Mortimer, Jack Riegelhuth, Ted Waller}} || {{dts|1933|August|2}} || <small>Secor</small> |----- | {{sort|LeConte, Mount|[[Mount Le Conte (California)|Mount Le Conte]]}} || {{convert|13930|ft|m|disp=table}} || || 3 || {{sortname|Norman|Clyde}} || {{dts|1935|June}} || <small>Secor</small> |----- | [[North Dome]] || {{convert|7542|ft|m|disp=table}} || [[Royal Arches Route (Yosemite)|Royal Arches Route]] || 5.10 || {{sort|Adam, Harris, Davis |Adam, Harris, Davis}} || {{dts|1936}} || <small>Roper; Steck</small> |----- | [[Lost Arrow Spire]] || {{convert|6930|ft|m|disp=table}} || [[Lost Arrow Spire Chimney|Spire Chimney]] || 5.10 || {{sort|Nelson, Ax, Salathé, John|Ax Nelson, [[John Salathé]]}} || {{dts|1947}} || <small>Roper; Steck</small> |----- | [[Sentinel Rock]] || {{convert|7038|ft|m|disp=table}} || [[Steck-Salathé Route (Sentinel Rock)|Steck-Salathe Route]] || {{sort|5.09|5.9}} || {{sort|Salathé, John, Steck, Allen|[[John Salathé]], [[Allen Steck]]}} || {{dts|1950}} || <small>Roper; Steck</small> |----- | [[Palisade Crest]] || {{convert|13559|ft|m|disp=table}} || Northwest ridge || 4 || {{sort|Jensen, Don, Jensen, Joan, Post, Rex|Don Jensen, Joan Jensen, Rex Post}} || {{dts|1969}} || <small>Secor</small> |}
