This is a list of television programs broadcast by [[Disney Channel (Canada)|Disney Channel]], a Canadian version of the [[Disney Channel|United States cable channel of the same name]]. Its French-language feed, [[La chaîne Disney]], has a slightly different schedule than the English-language version.
